<ab facs="#facs_232_r2l4"><expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> wegen . die leipgeding von euch <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . Darümb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_r2l5"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> willen beſant </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_r2l6">vnd cʒurede geſacʒt / vnd die <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vns <expan>geantvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / daʒ ſie </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_r2l7">euch ſelber an Jrem brief ein antvvurtt <expan>ſchreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_r2l9">
